OL,3,CCumberland adult social care 'requires
OL,4,Cimprovement'
OL,6,F"We found people were waiting too long
OL,7,Ffor occupational therapy assessments,
OL,8,Fequipment, financial assessments and
OL,9,Fannual reviews, with people with a
OL,10,Flearning disability waiting the
OL,11,Flongest for their review.
OL,13,F"There was also limited access to
OL,14,Fspecialist support for people with
OL,15,Fmental health needs, dementia or a
OL,16,Flearning disability, which meant
OL,17,Ffamilies could have to travel further
OL,18,Faway to see their loved one.
