OL,6,FCllr Lisa Hinton, Cumberland Council
OL,7,FExecutive Member for Adult Social
OL,8,FCare, said: "The assessment highlights
OL,9,Fthe strengths of our services and
OL,10,Fareas where we can continue to improve.
OL,12,F"Since the assessment, we have
OL,13,Fstrengthened support for unpaid
OL,14,Fcarers, expanded respite provision
OL,15,Facross Cumberland, and enhanced the
OL,16,Fquality and responsiveness of our
OL,17,Fservices.
